lead_paragraph: THE NEW ARCHBISHOR.--The Philadelphia Catholic Herald gives the true version of the story that the See of Baltimore had been made an Archbishopric: "During the past week, various, rumors have been circulated respecting the filling of the vacant see of Baltimore, which have caused many anxious inquiries.
